{"tid":640530,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"全港學校下星期二停課","createTime":"2018-04-24T10:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T10:55:06.000Z","uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4cb08daee091fa9b5be6ee471517da9ab1c38630","tid":640530,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:42:53.000Z","msg":"消息指，下週二（1日)幼稚園和小學及中學停課。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本港過去曾因流感襲擊兒童危機升級而要宣布停課，2008年，有鑑於本港出現多宗兒童死於甲型H1流感個案，當局宣布提早於3月13日起開始放復活節假期，至3月28日止。<br />\n<br />\n2008年，一名3歲男童因流感惡化正接受深切治療，加上7歲男童羅浩明證實死於甲型 H1流感病毒，當局晚上急急拍板全港小學及幼稚園即時停課兩周，推翻12小時前宣佈不須停課的說法。"},{"pid":"acfdef1277bc53d336ac80a70a31550433c9581e","tid":640530,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:54:26.000Z","msg":"無得返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029f0c184f7b0c8fc5f4a36e7da300b445c17eba","tid":640530,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:55:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1/5/2018</span></span>"}]}